She growled as she watched Tyrael, then noticed Hydras. Almost growling, she 
didn't need porotection, she wanted to feel the ripping apart of another bot 
at her claws once more... it had been so long. To taste the fluids & fuels, the 
whole sensation of terminating another pulsing through her circuits. 

"Let me at him, Hydras," she growled & hissed in pain bettween her razor 
teeth. "I want to show him what pain REALLY is!" Her 2 weapons at ready, begging 
for a chance at the supposed transformer.
